# Arrays - Data Structures & Algorithms

This folder contains **Array-based problems** and their solutions.

## 📚 Topics Covered

- Two Sum
- Maximum Subarray
- Merge Sorted Arrays
- Remove Duplicates
- Rotate Array
- and more...

## 📝 How to Add Problems

1. Create a subfolder with problem name: `mkdir TwoSum`
2. Add `Solution.java` with the implementation
3. Add `README.md` with:
   - Problem description
   - Examples
   - Approach/Algorithm
   - Time & Space Complexity
   - Test cases

## 🚀 Example Structure

```
Arrays/
├── TwoSum/
│   ├── Solution.java
│   ├── README.md
│   └── TestCases.java
├── MaximumSubarray/
│   ├── Solution.java
│   ├── README.md
│   └── TestCases.java
```

